{"tid":2515250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲報告：疫苗副作用：眼疾，包括失明","createTime":"2021-05-03T23:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T00:55:32.000Z","uid":294518,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c170ebb01ae3f326f88f1128308ce5a69e3036","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:58:32.000Z","msg":"歐洲報告：疫苗副作用：眼疾，包括失明<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVn6EK5xBv9oTfnPKhtJ2FUKVK7oZ43BW5Q8uUSSCSAxv?filename=5T1yR2o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5T1yR2o.png&h=706bd1d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://humansarefree.com/2021/05/eye-disorders-including-blindness-following-covid-vaccines.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhumansarefree.com%2F2021%2F05%2Feye-disorders-including-blindness-following-covid-vaccines.html&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=701f4774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://humansarefree.com/2021/05/eye-disorders-including-blindness-following-covid-vaccines.html</a>"},{"pid":"c31d100f7ef8b5388cd000278c168863c56a0e7e","tid":2515250,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"小眾極右網"},{"pid":"0ba768f286b3376961533cc53e89406b71fa6ecf","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:01:01.000Z","msg":"在向世界衛生組織歐洲藥物監測機構提交的19,916份注射實驗性COVID-19疫苗後的「眼部疾病」報告中，有數百個失明病例。<br />\n<br />\n由瑞典烏普薩拉監測中心 (UMC) 維護的VigiBase是世界衛生組織的全球個人病例安全報告數據庫。向VigiBase報告的近2萬種眼部疾病中，有超過一半的眼部疾病（10,667例）也被報告給了英國的黃卡不良事件報告系統。但是，VigiBase和黃卡報告並沒有提供患者的不良副作用的細節。這些被報告的眼部疾病包括：<br />\n<br />\n眼痛 (4616例)<br />\n視力模糊 (3839例)<br />\n畏光或不耐光 (1808例)<br />\n視力障礙 (1625例)<br />\n眼睛腫脹 (1162例)<br />\n眼部充血或紅眼 (788例)<br />\n眼部刺激 (768例)<br />\n眼睛發癢或眼部瘙癢 (731例)<br />\n眼睛流淚或流淚增多 (653例)<br />\n復視或復視現象 (559例)<br />\n眼睛疲勞或弱視 (459例)<br />\n乾眼症 (400例)<br />\n眼睛周圍腫脹或眼眶周圍腫脹 (366例)<br />\n眼瞼腫脹 (360例)<br />\n視野中的閃光或畏光 (358例)<br />\n失明 (303例)<br />\n眼瞼水腫 (298例)<br />\n眼睛或眼球不適 (273例)<br />\n結膜出血或眼小血管破裂 (236例)<br />\n眼瞼痙攣或眼部肌肉的異常收縮 (223例)<br />\n玻璃體漂浮物 (192例)<br />\n眼眶周圍水腫 (171例)<br />\n眼部出血 (169例子)<br />\n這些報告主要是在注射阿斯利康和輝瑞的COVID-19疫苗之後發出的。其中在有關莫德納（Moderna）疫苗的228份報告中，包括了8份眼部疾病的報告，然而截至4月21日，該疫苗首劑才僅僅注射了10萬份。<br />\n<br />\n在僅獲得緊急使用授權（EUA）的疫苗的臨床試驗中，並沒有關於眼部疾病的報告。"},{"pid":"cbb89df54ee0dab0dd5e71e2471ee53bcb77454c","tid":2515250,"uid":142854,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:03:23.000Z","msg":"你擝個搪尿痛人打疾苗之後屈返個疾苗有副作用有咩意思？？？"},{"pid":"aef4e1ac803c316acf785dbe203d04f3c02c72c8","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"美國食品和藥物管理局為管理輝瑞公司實驗性疫苗的人提供的概況介紹也並沒有提到眼睛的副作用。然而，它的確指出，「隨著輝瑞-生物技術公司COVID-19疫苗的更廣泛使用，可能會出現其他不良反應，其中一些可能很嚴重的」。<br />\n<br />\n賓夕法尼亞州的免疫學家胡曼-努爾查什姆（Hooman Noorchashm）警告說，為20%至30%已經有過近期或潛在的COVID感染的人接種疫苗可能會導致災難性的事件。"},{"pid":"424846edd2eeb141e18b4ddc289e1912f72563da","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:07:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vigiaccess.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vigiaccess.org%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=eaa541d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vigiaccess.org/</a>"},{"pid":"1b4d79968cdaeee88bedc243418ab1da3a9d53fb","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"424846edd2eeb141e18b4ddc289e1912f72563da","tid":2515250,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:07:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.vigiaccess.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vigiaccess.org%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnoHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=eaa541d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vigiaccess.org/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRX7vAcvagJztxJuTkFHVHtZ8BGXZg6G3zrcyed4o5nwr?filename=gAyQUjq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAyQUjq.png&h=5771bfb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2499b1fe79c8ec50811b4e775a150984f81ca265","tid":2515250,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"More than half of the eye disorders (10,667) were also reported to the U.K.&rsquo;s Yellow Card adverse event reporting system.<br />\n<br />\nThese would have followed injection primarily of AstraZeneca&rsquo;s and Pfizer&rsquo;s COVID-19 vaccines but included eight reports of eye disorders among the 228 reports concerning Moderna&rsquo;s vaccine, of which only 100,000 first doses had been administered by April 21.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實% 好撚低，  英國第一針有三千幾萬人，你話20，000有事。"},{"pid":"4b647127d93848dbafa7f479ee61c8854495e7f5","tid":2515250,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"咁你唔去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a3dd48d01b132d374cf0f3e49963566e05697b","tid":2515250,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31d100f7ef8b5388cd000278c168863c56a0e7e","tid":2515250,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"小眾極右網"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:54:08.000Z","msg":"極右都唔係<br />\n純粹陰謀論網"},{"pid":"34703a24a4b9f9ca2d5a6ecc5f4466cbd5e17e06","tid":2515250,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a3dd48d01b132d374cf0f3e49963566e05697b","tid":2515250,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31d100f7ef8b5388cd000278c168863c56a0e7e","tid":2515250,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:00:18.000Z","msg":"小眾極右網"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:54:08.000Z","msg":"極右都唔係<br />\n純粹陰謀論網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T00:55:32.000Z","msg":"樓主唔解釋下嘅話當放流料block得"}]}